result.execSummary:
The defendant Tina M Manthe was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Tina M Manthe is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Tina M Manthe was found guilty of Burglary-Building or Dwelling, a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 943.10(1m)(a).
